Source: R/utils.R
rxStateOde.Rd

Get the ODE states only

Usage

rxStateOde(obj)

Arguments

obj

rxode2 object

Value

ODE states only

Author

Matthew L. Fidler

Examples


mod <- rxode2({
  Cp <- linCmt(Cl, V, Q2, V2, Q3, V3)
  ke0 <- log(2)/(50)
  d/dt(Ce) <- (Cp-Ce)*ke0
})
